headline: How Recent Developments Are Rewriting the Story for GE HealthCare Technologies
summary: Consensus analyst price targets for GE HealthCare Technologies have slipped modestly, easing from $88 to about $86.96 per share in the latest round of updates. This shift reflects the latest market research, balancing optimism over the company’s solid operational results with continued caution tied to the unpredictable global economic environment.
